{"tid":1750750,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"助選團成員疑違規拉票　周浩鼎：不清楚情況","createTime":"2019-11-24T13:29:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T13:29:41.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6c98e9c3d3d7c668c2509d0f19a1ecdad0199901","tid":1750750,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/11/facebook_20190425-CR-%E5%91%A8%E6%B5%A9%E9%BC%8E1-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F11%2Ffacebook_20190425-CR-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25B5%25A9%25E9%25BC%258E1-1.png&h=3a7fe48f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n疑違規帶人進入「禁止拉票區」拉票。<br />\n<br />\n區議會選舉投票今日舉行，各區的候選人亦到處拉票。在東涌南選區，周浩鼎助選團成員疑違規帶人進入禁止拉票區拉票。爭取連任的周浩鼎其後在回應時表示，不清楚情況。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/11/20191124_PO_%E5%91%A8%E6%B5%A9%E9%BC%8E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F11%2F20191124_PO_%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25B5%25A9%25E9%25BC%258E.jpg&h=f66f095a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周浩鼎指，不清楚情況，並批評政府排隊安排混亂。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n在東涌南的票站外，一名身穿周浩鼎助選團背心的女子，下午帶着一名老伯進入票站範圍的禁止拉票區，並指示老伯排隊，其後自行離開票站。有在場記者向她詢問相關事件，該名女子並無回應提問並嘗試脫下身上的助選團背心。有目擊者則指，聽到該女子向該名老伯指：「投一號」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/04/facebook_20190425-CR-%E5%91%A8%E6%B5%A9%E9%BC%8E1-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F04%2Ffacebook_20190425-CR-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25B5%25A9%25E9%25BC%258E1-1.jpg&h=6d50199f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周浩鼎（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n周浩鼎其後在回應時表示，不清楚情況，並批評政府排隊安排混亂，導致多名長者及坐輪椅人士需輪候較長時間，並感到身體不適。<br />\n<br />\n東涌南選區候選人還有劉永賢、黎永安，以及報稱獨立的王進洋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/5476364-%E3%80%90%E5%8D%80%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E3%80%91%E5%8A%A9%E9%81%B8%E5%9C%98%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E7%96%91%E9%81%95%E8%A6%8F%E5%85%A5%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E6%8B%89%E7%A5%A8%E5%8D%80%E6%8B%89%E7%A5%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F5476364-%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%258A%25A9%25E9%2581%25B8%25E5%259C%2598%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%2581%2595%25E8%25A6%258F%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%25A6%2581%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E6%258B%2589%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%258B%2589%25E7%25A5%25A8&d=8H50EXT8eKO%2B303r5eJ0KJ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=139335cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/5476364-%E3%80%90%E5%8D%80%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E3%80%91%E5%8A%A9%E9%81%B8%E5%9C%98%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E7%96%91%E9%81%95%E8%A6%8F%E5%85%A5%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E6%8B%89%E7%A5%A8%E5%8D%80%E6%8B%89%E7%A5%A8</a>"}]}